headline: Bonobos Owner Nears Deal for Wedding-Dress Brand Vera Wang
summary: WHP Global is nearing a deal to purchase the Vera Wang brand, which brings in over $700 million in annual retail sales, according to people familiar with the matter.

headline: These Five Wall Street Titans Thought Bitcoin Was a Fad. Here’s What They Say Now.
summary: Bitcoin, the world’s largest cryptocurrency, is ascendant in Washington and a $2 trillion asset. Yet some of the most astute investors still aren’t convinced of its value.
